Title: CBT Reflection Note: Overcoming Career Worries
Date: 2026-06-15
Source: mira_015_cbt_reflection_note.pdf
Demo Persona: Mira Vale
Privacy Level: private

I had a sudden thought that I'm not making fast enough progress in my career. I stopped and wrote down the evidence: I've successfully completed three major client projects in the last six months, and received excellent feedback. Career growth is a gradual journey, and the evidence shows I am moving forward.